{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Establish a statutory body to mediate disputes within the motor industry.",
        "additional_details": "We think the National Conciliation Service has not accurately fulfilled this role and they provide an exceptionally bad service to the public.\r\n\r\nWe think we need a reliable statutory body instead, who would protect the customers and would genuinely step into the disputes.",
        "background": "Set up a Statutory Body for mediation purposes for customers of the motor industry as a board that would act as a medium between parties. We think the panel of the board should be vetted and required to actively communicate with complainants throughout the process.",
